---
import Group from '../assets/images/group.png';
---

<section data-bg="lab" class="section-shell py-24">
  <div class="max-w-[1700px] mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
    <div class="text-center md:text-left">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight">
        We test products for <br />
        <span class="text-[#ef4444]">accuracy</span>,
        <span class="text-[#ef4444]">heavy metals</span>, <br />
        and <span class="text-[#ef4444]">microbes</span>
      </h2>

      <p class="mt-8 text-gray-400 text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-lg mx-auto md:mx-0">
        A concerning finding is the presence of a diverse array of contaminants in these products.
        This highlights the importance of thorough testing and quality control measures to ensure
        consumer safety and product purity.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-10 flex justify-center md:justify-start">
        <a href="/products" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-[#2563eb] hover:bg-blue-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold transition-all">
          Explore products
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 3.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l6 6a1 1 0 010 1.414l-6 6a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L14.586 11H3a1 1 0 110-2h11.586l-4.293-4.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative h-full min-h-105 md:min-h-135 flex items-center justify-center">
      <div aria-hidden="true" class="hidden"></div>

      <img
        src={Group.src}
        width={Group.width}
        height={Group.height}
        alt="Ilustración de resultados de laboratorio de productos"
        class="relative z-10 drop-shadow-[0_28px_70px_rgba(0,0,0,0.45)]"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
